AMAX Inc said it has filed foran offering of 15,757,350 common shares, including 757,300 tobe sold by Mitsui and Co Ltd &lt;MITSY>.    AMAX said it will offer 12,607,350 shares in the U.S.through underwriters led by First Boston Inc &lt;FBC>, along withAmerican Express Co's &lt;AXP> Shearson Lehman Brothers Incsubsidiary, &lt;Goldman, Sachs and Co> and Merrill Lynch and CoInc &lt;MER>.    Remaining shares will be sold outside the U.S. throughunderwriters led by First Boston's Credit Suisse First BostonLtd affiliate, Shearson, Goldman Sachs and Merrill Lynch.    AMAX said it will use its proceeds to reduce revolvingcredit debt and repurchase or repay from time to time otherdebt. Reuter&#3;